# Server-side
<reply>
<servercmd>
connection-monitor
</servercmd>

# this is returned first since we get no proxy-auth
<data>
HTTP/1.1 407 Authorization Required to proxy me my dear
Proxy-Authenticate: Digest realm="weirdorealm", nonce="12345"
Content-Length: 33

And you should ignore this data.
</data>

# then this is returned when we get proxy-auth
<data1000>
HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Length: 21
Server: no

Nice proxy auth sir!
</data1000>

<datacheck>
HTTP/1.1 407 Authorization Required to proxy me my dear
Proxy-Authenticate: Digest realm="weirdorealm", nonce="12345"
Content-Length: 33

HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Length: 21
Server: no

Nice proxy auth sir!
HTTP/1.1 407 Authorization Required to proxy me my dear
Proxy-Authenticate: Digest realm="weirdorealm", nonce="12345"
Content-Length: 33

HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Length: 21
Server: no

Nice proxy auth sir!
</datacheck>
</reply>

